{"article_id":"XvTYjNBCWNFWcbUt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Sen. Ted Cruz","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"( R-TX )","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"could have defeated Donald Trump for the Republican nomination -","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"if Sen. Marco Rubio","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"( R-FL )","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"had joined his ticket as his vice presidential candidate ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"according to Cruz campaign officials","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"quoted by CNN Sunday .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Top officials of the Cruz campaign are convinced","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"there is one specific step","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that could have stopped Trump","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"-","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"and they blame Sen. Marco Rubio","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"for not taking that step .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"In early March , it became clear that Trump was well on his way to the nomination","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"and would even likely defeat Rubio in his home state of Florida ' s March 15 primary .","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"According to several sources close to Cruz ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"the Cruz campaign conducted several secret polls","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to see what the impact would be","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"if Rubio joined Cruz as his running mate , with Cruz at the top of the ticket .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"The result of those polls was a \" blowout \" for Cruz ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"according to the Cruz officials .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Rubio dropped out on March 15 ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"after losing in his home state of Florida","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"- but not before taking votes in several states","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that arguably might have gone to Cruz instead of Trump .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"( Rubio supporters likewise saw Cruz as a spoiler for their candidate . )","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"On March 21 , Politico broke the news","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"that Cruz had , indeed , approached Rubio with a proposal for a \" unity ticket , \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"but the Florida Senator had refused .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Doug Deason , a Cruz supporter","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"who volunteered to act as a go-between ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"told Politico :","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"\" Rubio was too pompous","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to act on it .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"He believed his own internal polls","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and there was no swaying him away from staying in the race through the Florida primary ...","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"If he had signed on before the first Super Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Cruz would have won all of the Texas votes and a lot more delegates .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"They may have very well won Florida . \"","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"The week before Cruz lost the Indiana primary ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"and dropped out of the race ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"he and Ohio Gov . John Kasich had announced a pact","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"to divide up the remaining primary states before California","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"- a pact","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Kasich broke soon afterwards ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"stumping in Indiana .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Cruz eventually named former Hewlett-Packard CEO and presidential candidate Carly Fiorina as his running mate","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"- a move","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that generated headlines","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"that partially blunted the effect","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"of crushing losses in the northeast states ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"but did not reverse his overall decline .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Trump led polls throughout the Republican primary campaign ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"but typically lost in head-to-head polls against individual candidates .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Joel B. Pollak is Senior Editor-at-Large at .","depth":2},{"id":56,"text":"His new e-book , Leadership Secrets of the Kings and Prophets :","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"What the Bible ' s Struggles Teach Us About Today ,","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"is on sale through Amazon Kindle Direct .","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"Follow him on Twitter at @ joelpollak .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":119,"left":114,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":73,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":67,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":65,"right":66,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":62,"right":64,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":62,"left":61,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":61,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":63,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":63,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":70,"left":69,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":8,"right":68,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":74,"right":112,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":84,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":79,"right":83,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":77,"right":78,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":16,"right":76,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"paren